In doing so, the entire group benefits from the growing production of Airbus and Boeing, which accounts for 85 percent of sales.
He expects average order growth of four percent a year until 2017.
In the custom book, it has orders for 2.6 billion euros, equivalent to four-year production.
French media say Latecoere can finally breathe again after years on drips.
